        Embrace nature's beauty with our exquisite collection of botanical wonders. Explore now for a serene experience!
        <br /> <br />
        <button class="btn btn-primary button">
            <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Plants" asp-action="Index">Get Started!</a>
